 data-ver="1.0" data-id="1654090644203" style=""><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-align="left" data-exc=""><hr class="gf_separator"></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1673519662261" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1" data-id="1673519662261" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;"><br></span></h2><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><ly-as-1192475>Skin Care Tips & Notes</ly-as-1192475></h2></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1596980964922" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1596980964922"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><div><strong><ly-as-1192476>As we come to the end of the 10 Steps, please remember that the 10 Steps are just guidelines.&nbsp;</ly-as-1192476></strong><br></div><div><br></div><div><ly-as-1192477>No one is required to do all 10 Steps. And doing all 10 Steps will not always guarantee you perfect, glass skin.</ly-as-1192477></div><div><br></div><div><ly-as-1192478>The most important thing is to find a routine that works for you, whether that be 3 steps, 5 steps, 10 steps, or somewhere in-between! Everyone's skin is different, and everyone's lifestyles are different.&nbsp;</ly-as-1192478></div><div><br></div><div><ly-as-1192479>The fun and joy of skincare comes from trying new things, testing out new products, and finding new and exciting ways to take care of our skin. Let this article be a starting point for you on your skincare journey. And along that journey, we encourage you to take all of the freedoms and liberties you want in your skincare routine because it's YOURS. Be patient with yourself, and the results will come.&nbsp;</ly-as-1192479></div><div><br></div><div><ly-as-1192480>Overall, remember you're already beautiful. We at Korean Skincare believe in doing skincare because we're all about showing our skin we care.&nbsp;</ly-as-1192480></div><div><br></div><div><ly-as-1192481>Love,&nbsp;</ly-as-1192481></div><div><ly-as-1192482>KS Team</ly-as-1192482></div><div><br></div></div></div><div data-label="Separator" data-key="separator" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1653640191910" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-separator" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1653640191910"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-align="left" data-exc=""><hr class="gf_separator"></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1653641854799" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1653641854799" data-layout-lg="3+9" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="3+9" data-layout-sm="3+9" data-layout-xs="12+12"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-3 gf_col-md-3 gf_col-sm-3 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1653641854829" data-id="1653641854829"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1653641932709" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1653641932709" data-resolution="3000x3000" style=""><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/494ac25e-0853-4776-89b0-2a7b2e3bd713/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/1080x1080-Pink.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="75%" data-height="auto" title="" width="1080" height="1080" natural-width="1080" natural-height="1080"></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-9 gf_col-md-9 gf_col-sm-9 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1653641924038" data-id="1653641924038"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1653641939748" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1